        </acqinfo>
        <odd id="ref4">
            <head>General note</head>
            <p>Another copy of this journal, worded differently, was edited by Anthony F. C. Wallace and published in 
                <emph render="italic">Pennsylvania History</emph> 19 (1952): 177, 325.</p>
        </odd>
        <bioghist id="ref2">
            <head>Biographical/Historical note</head>
            <p>Halliday Jackson was a Pennsylvania Quaker missionary to the Indians.</p>
        </bioghist>
